。","index":19,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"e645180fb2","type":"paragraph","text":"从那以后我们学了点东西，变得聪明些了！","index":20,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"b37bb72805","type":"paragraph","text":"但是也必须注意到现在情况不同了一一当时共产党人在任何地方都没有掌权","index":21,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"916b5da7e5","type":"paragraph","text":"现在有苏联！","index":22,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"714868a9bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）共产党不应该是宣传小组，而应该是工人阶级的政党。","index":23,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"6a73dfc235","type":"paragraph","text":"现在不是研究理论的时候！","index":24,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"73e71e24c2","type":"paragraph","text":"需要的是动员群众进行斗争。","index":25,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"b8f2e47308","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为，我们在（与爱沙尼亚、立陶宛、拉脱维亚缔结的）互助条约中找到了我们能够把许多国家置于苏联影响范围之内的形式。但是，为了能够坚持下去，我们必须严格维护它们的国内制度和独立。我们不谋求它们的苏维埃化。它们自己进行苏维埃化的时候会到来的。《季米特落关日记选编》","index":26,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"1b7c4fddd2","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》2002年版第101-102页","index":27,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"},{"id":"67542e1493","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷干第12-13页","index":28,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0"}],"page":{"id":"e2a586c95f","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"0522dd42a0","start":2759,"end":2760}}}},"__N_SSG":true}